				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Moned</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5596963</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Is that a new esoteric class I spot? ;p</p> <p>Saw this in thecritters chat and liked it a lot. The effort level is great and coupled with the story as a whole I love it. For me, it kind of reminds me of Terry Pratchett Small Gods (If you haven't read that I would hugely recommend) and the way gods grow in power due to belief.</p> <p>I very much look forward to seeing more from you in the future!</p> 
				 	]]>
